headline: 3 Unusually Active Cash-Secured Puts in Quality Companies for Attractive Income
summary: There were 433 unusually active put options on Wednesday, including 34 with Vol/OI ratios of 10.0 or more. Many were higher-risk, money-losing businesses. However, there were three quality companies worth selling cash-secured puts for attractive income.
